data: {"type":"tool_result","toolUseId":"item_4","content":"264:    .contact-panel { background: var(--fg); color: var(--on-primary); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: clamp(26px, 5vw, 44px); }\n265:    .contact-panel .lead, .contact-panel .meta { color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--on-primary) 74%, var(--muted)); }\n266:    .contact-panel .input, .contact-panel .textarea, .contact-panel .select { background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 96%, var(--fg)); }\n267:    .contact-lines { display: grid; gap: 12px; }\n268:    .contact-lines a { text-decoration: underline; text-decoration-thickness: 1px; text-underline-offset: 4px; }\n314:        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n345:            <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"#contact\">Send details</a>\n382:            <p>A simple contact route for roofing issues that do not fit neatly into one service category.</p>\n398:          <p class=\"lead\">The page gives homeowners enough structure to act: service area, contact details, roofing services, and a clear inspection-first next step.</p>\n400:            <li>Verified contact details stay visible and easy to use.</li>\n416:          <p class=\"lead\">Material visuals support the main conversion path: understand the roofing issue, contact M&amp;B Roofing, and arrange the next step.</p>\n471:    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"contact\" id=\"contact\">\n473:        <div class=\"contact-panel stack\">\n474:          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Contact</p>\n477:          <div class=\"contact-lines\">\n","isError":false}

